      <td>Physically one can develop coordination, gain strength, increase flexibility, and improve cardiovascular conditioning. From all of these physical practices one can have a strong body.</td>
      <td>Mentally one can build self-confidence, gain better judgement, and improve self-control from all these mental disciplines. One can have a sound mind.</td>
